  stimulus_text = 'The author argues that the world is becoming increasingly interconnected. This trend is evident in the way people communicate with one another.  Technology has made it possible for people to share their ideas and experiences with a wider audience, and as a result, the world has become a smaller place.  However, the author notes that this trend also presents challenges.  For example, the influx of information can be overwhelming and confusing, and it can be difficult to distinguish between reliable sources and misinformation. What is the most likely reason why the author states the world has become a smaller place?',
